Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:06.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sploosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dun-dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Synerg SP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the Century Legend\N Magical Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:28.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-Ma-Magical Destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:35.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Britney!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:40.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,By all appearances, I'm a fine florist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you interrupting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will have people wondering \Nwhat in the world is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it's a new opening sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new opening sequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to commemorate the 44th episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have decided to animate my manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we do something \Nsimilar once before, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, starting next week, \Nwe'll have it properly sung by Kotoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, please start \Nthe real opening sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:17.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:20.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and both have a bit of \Nthe wrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:34.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but they share the immensely strong, \Nloving bond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This episode of "Hayate the \NCombat Butler" is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is in no way related \Nto real people or organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:50.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:55.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:02:00.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:11.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:21.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:27.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:33.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:44.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:55.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mystery of the 120 \NEmployment Rate (Temp.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? It's the completed \Nversion of "Magical Destroy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always tell me it's hard to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I tried making it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem \Nthat different from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I restrained my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took it upon myself to make \Nrevisions targeting the masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you saying it's {\i1}still{\i0} \Nbeyond your comprehension?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is easy for you to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storminess of the Sea \Nof Japan here represents the ferocity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the battle that's about to start, see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fwahahaha, I have finally \Nfound you, Britney!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hm? That voice... \NSurely not! Who are you?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have come all this way to the \NSea of Japan to defeat you. I am..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...your enemy!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Damn it, my enemy, huh?!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Then, surely, I have \Nno choice but to fight!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's right!! You have \Nno choice but to fight!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But since you call yourself my enemy...!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You must be strong!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am not very strong!!! \NBecause I am an early enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this a game of "you lose \Nif you poke fun at this"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy has already \Nappeared on the 3rd page!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thrilling, suspenseful development!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's even saying himself \Nthat he's not strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this journey about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, Isumi, when did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's Isumi for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so very interesting that I tried \Nwriting the continuation to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Kitten's Life".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There was a kitten \Nwith wings flying in the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Upon inspecting it from various angles,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"it turns out it was going \Nat 23km per hour."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's incredible, Isumi! \NThis is the feel I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're at it again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sakuya. And when did {\i1}you{\i0} get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those two incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, their conversation is just \Nso out there in another dimension...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. And they understand each \Nother, so it's really somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really that hard to draw a manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if your art is decent \Nand the story is carefully told,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have a reasonable chance \Nat winning prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make problematic statements like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, you've won \Na manga award before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have yet to read your manga, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to read it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, not that I mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My name is Britney."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As you can see, I'm an energetic \Npart-timer at a flower shop."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Normally, I'm making a mess of things, \Nenticed by the scent of flowers."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ROOOAAAARRR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So I'm always getting \Nchewed out by the owner."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But enticed by the sweet scent \Nof those flowers come the bad guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But it's no problem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I make short work of guys like \Nthat with my magic!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's right, I'm secretly a magical girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The magical girl of flowers, Britney!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This manga plays it so safe, \Nit actually kinda ticks me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's colored to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the art is adorable, but there is \Nsomething unwholesome about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't seem \Nto be very well-received.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it is aiming \Nto be popular from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? With a mocking style like \Nthis that's pretending to curry favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you can fool the judges,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't be able to \Nimpress the true readers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what happens \Nin your manga after this, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm still in the middle \Nof laying out the rest of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout ya at least tell us the plotline?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to know \Nwhat happens next, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not quite why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you leave me \Nno choice! I shall tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Emerging from the 12th dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:17.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,283)}*Illustrative Images
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,the great defeated warrior general, \Nalong with the dark defeated warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,turns all of humanity into worker ants \Nand tries to conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To do this, they first begin buying up \Nsugar in the futures market.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(91,155)} Futures Market
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to this, there's \Na worldwide shortage of sugar,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,so Britney hardens her resolve \Nto travel into the 8th dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she super loves cake \Nand stuff! Because she's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But Praying Mantisians come invading \Nright around then from nebula M2983
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:22.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,283)}Fan Service Images
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,with their eyes on Earth's \Npetroleum resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ancient Aztecs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, stop there, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop me?! \NIt was just getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that getting good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, if you don't figure out a way \Nto make it easier to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't get through to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup. It's all nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I was explaining it all to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, I was told that it \Nshould be around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, where in the world are we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.45,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen Taro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Animago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please take the table in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I will use the facilities here \Nto show you how fantastic my manga is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how in the world are you going to \Nuse the facilities of a ramen shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be that rumor I've heard...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, quick, quick, quick! Stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut 82, key animation work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to collect the finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash! Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Woohoo! But Dad's not here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key animation has been \Nchecked for performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rather anime-ish place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is an anime production studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the urban myth that anime studios \Ndisguise themselves as ramen shops,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hidin' at all costs from \Nthe general populace was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an urban myth like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, this show is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and in no way related \Nto the actual industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so this is where they make anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It totally has that "studio" feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we came here around \NEpisode 35, too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Miss Segawa, \NMiss Hanabishi, and Miss Asakaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, where are the voice actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, those people are over \Nat the recording studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're not here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought \NI'd get to meet Ms. Yahagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's really moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, I think \NI'll draw something up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.96,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Rip Roaring Student Council Tankenger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Maria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke. Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's just sleepin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll manage it somehow \Nby the end of the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not sleeping. She passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss, what \Nin the world are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have them animate \Nthe continuation of my manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Animate it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought it would be easier \Nto understand as an anime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than a verbal explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, doesn't the manga \Nusually have to succeed first,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before it gets animated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So exciting. So heart-pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued in the second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1}Te{\u0}rere, terere t{\u1}te{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is "terere" some kind of magical spell?\N({\u1}Te{\u0}rere tte nanika no jumon na{\u1}no{\u0}?)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, with this scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Unicron preying upon a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we won't be using \Nany CG and it'll all be drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be huge, like \Nthe climax scene in "Laputa",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then impressive like \Nthe opening of the "Patlabor" movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean the first movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to finish it off, we have \Nthe last scene from "Saint Seiya"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run through the crumbling temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is an explanation like this really \Ngoing to get across to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it in Mr. Shingo Araki's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Get it done in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think producing anime \Nis easy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper, whisper, whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will begin the production \Nwork right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagi, what the heck did ya do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. I didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it, since this \Ncompany will be making my anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was intel out there \Nthat their stock would probably go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So exciting. So exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to sound like a broken record, \Nbut this is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and is in no way related \Nto the actual industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:09.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, yet another anime \Nof questionable quality gets made...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to this show, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the storyboards still not done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's almost done,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the director said something \Nabout going to Toys 'R Us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to buy a limited edition figurine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send an assistant to do that! \NThis is part of their job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have quite a bit \Nof the design elements in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't have enough key animators!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble! The animation \Ndirector has suffered tenosynovitis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, we're short \Non animation staff members.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, you can't make the anime then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you poach them from other companies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kyoto Animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the anime based on Miss Nagi's \Noriginal work has entered production.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we'll make it in time somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've managed it \Nwithout casualties, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, a couple people collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess anime is a harsh industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The company doing the animation \Nand finishing work has fled overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it game over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, no choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, \Nwe will have to utilize {\i1}that{\i0} method!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world do you plan to do, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I have for dinner today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,102)}Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we've dropped the color \Nfrom the hamster's scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can shuffle over \Nas many staff members as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mean, Little Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called an outline take.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the art isn't done by the time \Nthey record the audio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they make this working footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho, so it's like a making-of film
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the general audience never gets to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I had no idea this \Nwas how they made anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.12,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,102)}Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,102)}Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,102)}Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the schedule gets tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll sometimes use art \Nfrom the planning stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may also just use \Nthe storyboards as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:28.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,102)}Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or show only a line made \Nwith a colored marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole lot of various ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't use film anymore, \Nso this no longer happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outline takes are so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty much how it looks \Nwhen we're recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that's a taboo topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we do that because we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, we'd like the recording \Nfootage to be in full color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and a bigger budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:59.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete Magical Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll leave the inside stories at that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the anime was finally completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get nervous somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So exciting. So heart-pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to cry 3 times during this film!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see what kinda secret \Ntreasure outrageous anime it's become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So heart-pounding. So exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have come to this point, \Nlet us brace ourselves for the worst, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May as well be hung for a sheep as a lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello to all the 130 million \NGirl A's across the nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, at Animate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're holding the super popular \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the merchandise \Nin your passionate fists
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and slam it down at the cashier along \Nwith the contents of your wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Toranoana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what are all these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie-ins. Since it's a rare opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd get some commercials, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Synerg SP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}End of the Century Legend \NMagical Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:15.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-Ma-Magical Destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:21.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Britney!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:27.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,By all appearances, I'm a fine florist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:32.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is I'm a magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:39.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Original work by Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:45.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A promising new author the entire \Nuniverse has been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:55.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With a cute heart and a cheery mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Britney is always gazing \Nupon her senpai from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,258)}Britney
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with this art?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made lunch, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sounds good. I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Britney is desperately \Nin love with her senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but, but, she can't tell him how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's a magical girl. \NNo, that's not the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because her senpai has... \N Because her senpai has...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:35.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(169,292)}Child
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:35.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,293)}Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a wife and child already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This turn of events \Nis actually really quite shocking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not sold on the art, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, because \Nof the evil witch's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the more it sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...her senpai was turned into a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to this, his wife fell ill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and his child became a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm in danger of losing \Nan online match, cut the connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension's building \Nmore than I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:15.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Britney resolves to turn her \Nsenpai back to how he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if she can accomplish this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,her senpai will only return to his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He and Britney will never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she continues this journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:31.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,she will get to spend time with \Nher senpai. Even though he's a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What will she do? What will Britney do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And Britney's decision was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A Kitten's Life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Kitten's Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tmp, tmp, tmp, tmp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tmp, tmp, tmp, tmp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running speed is mach 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how fast you run, \Nyou can never reach the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really are a genius, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you now \Nat least see how my manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you are also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are asking if I am "also", \Ndoes that mean you are also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought I would read \Nthe Miss's manga one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she worked so hard \Nto write it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we should try to understand her better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I was rather curious \Nto know what happens after that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Britney and her senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you suppose Britney \Nwill choose in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she wish to be with him? Or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like Nagi hasn't \Nwritten past that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose that means the Miss \Nis having a hard time deciding as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As to how to end this romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it were you, which would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that senpai were you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it wouldn't be bad to keep you \Nin the shape of a star forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then you try writing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never drawn manga \Nor anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all the more reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I could not, Hayate. Please, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a man, I'll conquer all \Nthe heroines simultaneously!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so who is this, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please, "conquer all the heroines \Nsimultaneously"? What am I, a brute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem \Nwith that? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be sure to make your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now you try drawing it, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you are such an indecisive person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:22.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a story about how fiction \Nsometimes reflects reality and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew. We almost forgot the fan service shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, even the fan service \Nis too avant-garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy these \Nto take away the bad after-taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,These are not to make sure \Nthe episode is long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hayate the Combat Butler" \Nhas fantastic fan service!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:48.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be sure to watch again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Does this count as fan service?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:06.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:11.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:15.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:23.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:32.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:42.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:57.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:09.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council Girl Trio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lettering by Sayuri Yahagi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council girl \Ntrio's Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izumi Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Risa Asakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm Miki Hanabishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the fruit of our \Nfriendship and hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council girl \Ntrio's theme song is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song is perfect \Nfor broadcasting at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great to play it at cleaning time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also perfect for going \Nfor a drive with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even she'll fall head over heels \Nwith this song playing on the car stereo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also perfect \Nfor lonely people living alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might give you the energy to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting this week, we'll be showing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fan service scenes of ours \Nfor the next segments!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:23:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, it'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adieu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world are we \Ngoing out to all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:19.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder where.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:03.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to wait to get there to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:07.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we call it "Thank you \Nfor everything, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:09.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The big sister appreciation \Nday relaxation plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:11.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always working so hard for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:12.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying in a midtown hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.78,0:24:14.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,going to the spa and \Ngetting beauty treatments...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:16.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about work \Nand just sit back and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:20.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "It Is Maria Appreciation \NDay! In February (heart)".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It Is Maria Appreciation Day! In February
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:23.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Prism Flash on "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" again next time!
